係屬於中國的話，咁韓國、尼泊爾、越南通通都係中國領土啦"},{"pid":"4684107404dd1016acdc3f6677d54f2ef666a4c1","tid":638808,"uid":30370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T06:28:48.000Z","msg":"二戰末期，美軍佔領整個琉球群島。日本宣布投降後，美國在琉球設置軍隊控制政府。一九四六年二月，美軍還將已劃歸日本鹿兒島縣的奄美群島從日本政府管轄中劃分出來，由美國在琉球群島的軍政府管轄。一九七一年，美國和日本簽訂《移交琉球協議》，<span style=\"color: red;\">但移交的是行政治權而非主權。沖繩地位未定論，已成各界共識。</span><br />\n<br />\n咁咪即係琉球主櫂係美國lor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n獨唔獨要問美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc13c97679cad799fb62feda5d87fe75354887c2","tid":638808,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T06:45:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78d91d833650cdcb9fbc1be5b280d71e69112b75","tid":638808,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T08:05:30.000Z","msg":"琉球獨立，中國或成最大贏家"},{"pid":"71c4dcf4d403e3d662640c3c7ee55dd1e08285d8","tid":638808,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T08:25:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08a027d00f23ece0db5c0cb9769286052c1c64b6","tid":638808,"uid":56954,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T12:51:53.000Z","msg":"日本快d報仇<br />\n支持香港獨立"},{"pid":"c6242ef59686f3439418378b4512af38a0b353fc","tid":638808,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T14:03:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b543a691e7c80c5a51a839b7f17ed3ad0062f713","tid":638808,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T16:19:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03a3b8cc3df1cad30fb074